{"id":543922,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/【网络民议】但我还是买不起房/","date":"2016-11-03T07:52:42Z","modified":"2016-11-03T07:52:42Z","title":"【网络民议】但我还是买不起房","content":"<p>最近，王健林在讲述太原街万达广场建设运营故事的时候，因为经营出问题为了保障业主利益，赔了10个亿回购。然后对比了海尔砸冰箱事件，他说：我们比海尔伟大多了，海尔砸冰箱才几个钱，我们赔10亿多……</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/XDedR.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-543923\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/XDedR.jpg\" alt=\"xdedr\" width=\"500\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/XDedR.jpg 672w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/XDedR-287x300.jpg 287w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>对于王健林此言，海尔官方回应称：没算过（1985年）张瑞敏砸的76台冰箱对几乎发不出工资的海尔意味着什么，但现在知道为什么买不起房了。此条回复引发部分官微搭车营销“但我还是买不起房”和网友评论。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/iJk3L.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-543924\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/iJk3L.jpg\" alt=\"ijk3l\" width=\"500\" height=\"475\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/iJk3L.jpg 578w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/iJk3L-300x285.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 33%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-543922 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e